ont about how this is tied to health anxiety\u2014they might involve a specialist or provide tools like cognitive behavioral techniques tailored to medical fears. Sometimes, just that validation from an in-person assessment can break the cycle.\n- **Symptom relief in the interim:** If you haven't tried it yet, over-the-counter options like ibuprofen combined with caffeine (or Excedrin Migraine) might help more than plain pain relievers. Hydrate well and rest as much as possible.\n\nYou're taking a brave step by reaching out here, and I believe getting that professional evaluation will help more than anything else right now. What do you think about heading to urgent care today? Or if there's any other symptom or detail you haven't mentioned (like recent head injury or family history), that could help us refine this even further. I'm right here with you\u2014let's get you through this."
