iques like mindfulness apps, deep breathing, or even short-term anxiety relief strategies might help in the meantime. If this persists, talking to a mental health professional could be beneficial too.\n\nWhat are your thoughts on this? Do you have more details about the frequency of these headaches or any recent changes that might help us refine the plan? I'm here to support you every step of the way."
