ur informed consent to the risks, and emphasizing the emotional aspect. Many doctors are empathetic to patient anxiety and may accommodate if they feel it's appropriate after their own assessment.\n\nIf you'd like, I can help refine this script, suggest questions to ask the doctor, or even point you to resources like telemedicine services (e.g., Teladoc or your insurance's virtual care options) where you could get seen quickly. How else can I support you right now?"
