in, I can arrange a prescription for a triptan (like sumatriptan) and an anti-nausea medication\u2014let me know if you'd like me to send that to your pharmacy.\n- **More on that \"different\" feeling**: If you're open, sharing any additional details (e.g., has the pain changed location, or are there triggers/symptoms I haven't heard about?) could help us pinpoint if this warrants escalation.\n\nI want you to feel safe and confident in your care\u2014let's make sure we address this promptly. Would heading to urgent care work for you, or is there another way I can help right now?"
