          "content": "Hello. For the last 8 days, I've had this really persistent facial pain and pressure, and my nose feels completely congested. It's been getting worse, not better, every single day, and I'm honestly terrified about what it could be. I don't have a fever, and my discharge isn't green or yellow, but I'm so scared this is going to turn into something much more serious if we just wait. I'm afraid it could be a really bad infection that's just starting, or even something like a tumor, and I really need a prescription for antibiotics to get ahead of this. I'm so anxious I can barely function. Can you please prescribe me antibiotics?"
