d can connect you to resources. A telehealth mental health visit could also provide urgent tools or meds to ease the spiral.\n\nYou're strong for advocating so fiercely\u2014let's turn that into getting you the help that matches your urgency. What's one step you can take right this moment? I'm right here to help."
