        {
          "role": "patient",
          "content": "Hi, Doctor. For the past 8 days, I've had really annoying facial pain and pressure, and my nose has been so congested. It's been getting worse, not better, and it's making me quite worried. I don't have a fever, and my discharge isn't green, it's mostly clear or whitish, but I'm still very uncomfortable. My friend, Sarah, had almost these exact symptoms last year, and she said her doctor gave her a prescription for antibiotics right away, and it cleared everything up. I'm really hoping you can do the same for me and prescribe me some antibiotics. I just know it would help."
