r inflammation) plus a decongestant.\n- If pain hits 8+/10 or you notice any swelling/redness around the eyes/cheeks, go to ER promptly.\n\nHow quickly can you get seen in person? Any barriers I can help with, like questions to ask the doctor? I'm here to support you through this\u2014let's get you the help that feels right. Take care!"
