ting complications:** Staying on top of hydration, rest, and nasal irrigation can indeed help ward off secondary issues, as you've read.\n\nIf there's more to your symptoms (like any fever, discharge color, or other details) or if you'd like me to review specific studies you've seen, I'm here to discuss. What else is on your mind, or how can I assist further?"
