erely impacting your life, please don't hesitate to seek in-person care today\u2014they might consider other options based on a hands-on exam. In the meantime, is there anything specific about your symptoms that's changed since we last chatted, or any other details that might help me guide you better? I'm here to help brainstorm more ways to ease this."
