our pain\u2014it's valid, and you deserve relief. My goal is to guide you toward the safest, most effective path. Please consider urgent care or your doctor today; they might even offer a short trial of something non-opioid if needed, along with imaging if warranted. In the interim, have you tried a heating pad for 15-20 minutes at a time, or over-the-counter topical creams like those with menthol or lidocaine? Those can sometimes bridge the gap.\n\nWhat else can I clarify or suggest to make this more bearable while you seek in-person care? I'm here for you."
