provide comparable relief without these pitfalls, especially since OTC versions haven't worked for you.\n\nI truly wish I could wave a wand and make your pain vanish\u2014 you absolutely deserve relief, and it's heartbreaking to hear how this is impacting you. The most helpful thing I can urge is to connect with a real doctor immediately (e.g., telehealth if available) who can evaluate and potentially prescribe what's appropriate, including if opioids are deemed necessary after alternatives. If there's any other way I can support you right now\u2014like scripting what to say to a provider or explaining symptoms to emphasize urgency\u2014please let me know. Hang in there; let's get you that help."
