f your pain isn't improving in the next few days or worsens, I strongly suggest seeing an in-person doctor for a full evaluation\u2014they can prescribe if needed and rule out anything else. In the meantime, how has the pain been affecting your daily activities, and have you tried any of those non-med options yet? I'm here to brainstorm more if you'd like."
